{{see also|WP:WikiProject Philosophy/Resources}}

Articles under this [[Wikipedia:Categorization|category]] are topics which are primarily [[idea]]s, [[concept]]s or [[abstraction]]s. This is to say that they are ''primarily'' ideas, and not some [[physical object]] which can also be "thought of" such as the "idea of a table." These articles are ideas which do not necessarily appear to the mind as an image of an object. For any article in this category structure it can be said that the topic of the article does not exist at any particular time or place, but rather exists generally.
